data.description: Welcome to 705 Hill St, Lebanon, PA – a charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence that combines comfort and potential. This home offers a unique blend of convenience and opportunity, making it a perfect choice for those seeking a comfortable living space with a touch of versatility.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main floor boasts a convenient 1st-floor laundry, providing added ease to your daily routine. The well-designed layout flows seamlessly, creating a space that feels both spacious and functional.  The heart of the home is the cozy living area, perfect for relaxing with family or entertaining friends. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ensuring a delightful culinary experience for the household chef.  One of the standout features of this property is the covered patio – an ideal spot for enjoying outdoor meals, morning coffee, or simply unwinding after a long day. Imagine hosting gatherings with loved ones or creating a personal oasis to escape and relax.  Car enthusiasts and DIY enthusiasts will be thrilled by the detached heated and cooled 3-car garage. This mechanic special comes complete with a lift and air compressor, providing an excellent space for automotive projects and hobbyists alike. Whether you're a car enthusiast or simply in need of extra storage, this garage offers endless possibilities.  The property is situated in a convenient location, with amenities and services just a short distance away. Enjoy the peace and tranquility of the neighborhood while having easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment options.  Don't miss the chance to make 705 Hill St your new home. Embrace the potential, create lasting memories, and take advantage of the unique features that set this property apart. Schedule a showing today to experience all that this home has to offer.
